203
00:11:04,180 --> 00:11:06,900
And there's no mystery about the origin

204
00:11:06,900 --> 00:11:09,620
of information in biology.

205
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:14,100
So one thing to say about that immediately.

206
00:11:14,100 --> 00:11:17,340
