00:19:54,380 --> 00:19:56,220
10 years before their discovery,

379
00:19:56,220 --> 00:19:59,860
and his ideas throughout the 90s were pretty marginal in the field,

380
00:19:59,860 --> 00:20:01,460
nobody was very interested in them,

381
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:04,300
and you can look back at conference proceedings

382
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:07,140
and see the discussions after people's talks,

383
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:09,020
and there would be Mike Russell jumping up and saying,

