and your genes will do better if you kill yourself.

1261
01:00:33,180 --> 01:00:35,460
So how do you, if you're in this predicament

1262
01:00:35,460 --> 01:00:37,100
of being taken down by viruses,

1263
01:00:37,100 --> 01:00:38,700
how do you kill yourself?

1264
01:00:38,700 --> 01:00:40,700
The answer is you unplug the membrane.

1265
01:00:40,700 --> 01:00:42,500
You collapse the membrane potential.

1266
01:00:42,500 --> 01:00:43,620
That's what you do.

1267
01:00:43,620 --> 01:00:45,660
That will kill you in seconds.

1268
01:00:45,660 --> 01:00:47,700
So this is really bacterial death.

1269
01:00:47,700 --> 01:00:50,700
It's all about the membrane potential,

1270
01:00:50,700 --> 01:00:52,220
which makes me think,

1271
01:00:52,220 --> 01:00:55,140
when they paddle, I showed you them paddling around,

1272
01:00:55,140 --> 01:00:57,300
this is proton powered.

1273
01:00:57,300 --> 01:01:01,620
Again, all the behaviour that bacteria do,

1274
01:01:01,620 --> 01:01:04,140
all the import and export of things across that membrane

1275
01:01:04,140 --> 01:01:07,500
is all powered by that membrane potential.

1276
01:01:07,500 --> 01:01:10,100
So this is very much the life and death

1277
01:01:10,100 --> 01:01:13,100
of what bacterial cells are actually doing.

1278
01:01:13,100 --> 01:01:16,060
Now, this I think is the final slide.

1279
01:01:18,100 --> 01:01:22,460
We are made of more complex cells.

1280
01:01:22,460 --> 01:01:24,860
We're made of eukaryotic cells.

1281
01:01:24,860 --> 01:01:26,340
Eukaryotes have lots of mitochondria.

1282
01:01:26,340 --> 01:01:27,940
These are the same things I've been showing you.

1283
01:01:27,940 --> 01:01:30,780
These are all individual bacteria that became included

1284
01:01:30,780 --> 01:01:32,220
in a much larger cell,

1285
01:01:32,220 --> 01:01:34,980
or it became a larger cell in the end.

1286
01:01:34,980 --> 01:01:37,460
And they're all doing the same kind of thing,

1287
01:01:37,460 --> 01:01:38,940
but now they've got to speak to each other.

1288
01:01:38,940 --> 01:01:40,340
There's different ways they can do that.

1289
01:01:40,340 --> 01:01:41,940
They can fuse together and fission.

1290
01:01:41,940 --> 01:01:43,540
There's all kinds of things they do,

1291
01:01:43,540 --> 01:01:47,700
