1294
01:01:51,540 --> 01:01:54,380
And when we're digesting food and burning food,

1295
01:01:54,380 --> 01:01:55,700
it's going straight here.

1296
01:01:55,700 --> 01:01:58,980
So although this is the interface with the world,

1297
01:01:58,980 --> 01:02:01,020
really what's happening is going on here.

1298
01:02:01,020 --> 01:02:03,500
Any problems that we have in relation to the world,

1299
01:02:03,500 --> 01:02:06,660
