And again, I'm thinking that fields are one way

1303
01:02:13,940 --> 01:02:15,540
in which this can happen.

1304
01:02:15,540 --> 01:02:18,300
And then this is a single cell like an amoeba cell.

1305
01:02:18,300 --> 01:02:20,220
Then we have multicellular organisms,

1306
01:02:20,220 --> 01:02:22,060
and now we've got cells to bring together

1307
01:02:22,060 --> 01:02:23,580
all with these moving parts inside.

1308
01:02:23,580 --> 01:02:25,780
And finally, a central nervous system,

1309
01:02:25,780 --> 01:02:27,500
which amplifies all of this.

1310
01:02:27,500 --> 01:02:30,380
So the communications, the electrical communications

1311
01:02:30,380 --> 01:02:33,140
between single cells and their interface with the world,

1312
01:02:33,140 --> 01:02:35,100
becoming incorporated into larger cells,

1313
01:02:35,100 --> 01:02:37,780
incorporated into multicellular organisms,

1314
01:02:37,780 --> 01:02:39,420
and finally into a central nervous system.

1315
01:02:39,420 --> 01:02:41,820
This, I'm suggesting, is the substrate,

1316
01:02:41,820 --> 01:02:45,180
which gives rise in the end to the complexity

1317
01:02:45,180 --> 01:02:46,740
of our own consciousness.

